Title: Parameters
Description: traces — a stacktrace. Array(UInt64).size — an allocation size for memory profiling. (optional - default 1). UInt64.ptr — an allocation address. (optional - default 0). UInt64.

NoteIn the case where ptr != 0, a flameGraph will map allocations (size > 0) and deallocations (size < 0) with the same size and ptr.
Only allocations which were not freed are shown. Non mapped deallocations are ignored.
